<br />
<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="http://board.byuu.org/viewtopic.php?f=3&amp;t=403">http://board.byuu.org/viewtopic.php?f=3&amp;t=403</a><!-- m -->
<br />
<br />Feel free to comment here as well. I'm especially very interested in the opinions of people who have created actual hardware devices like the PowerPak on their opinions of the feasibility of making this device a reality, even in very small, limited numbers.
<br />
<br />I believe I can create the software needed to drive demand for the hardware, and I would be willing to invest a good amount of money into prototyping such a design.</div>

					
